Made from 100% non-GMO soyabean seeds, refined flour & wheat protein, and sourced from the best farmers across India and abroad. Our defatted soya noodle offers 48% protein, 1% fat, 10% fiber. It is ultra low in fat, low in carbs and diabetic friendly. All our products are tested in FSSAI & NABL approved labs every 12 months which ensures no variation, no adulteration and maintains the nutrient profile. Storage & Expiry Store in a cool dry place. Consume the product within 1 month after opening the pouch or transfer the contents to an air tight jar immediately for a longer shelf life. The product has an expiry date of 9 months from the month of packing.
